##
# /usr/local/bin/pip -> pip-3.8
#
#
##

0. Check the version of pip
pip -V

1. Install nose or pytest
    pip install nose
    pip install pytest

2. Check the version of nose or pytest
    pip show nose
    pip show pytest

3. Run the test using nose
    nosetests

4. Run the test using pytest
    pytest

4.1 Only Run the one case in the test file
pytest test_hello_world.py::test_hello_world1
